== 螺線排列的數學模型 ==
{{main|费马螺线|黄金分割率}}
[[Image:SunflowerModel.svg|thumb]]
1979年由H. Vogel提出，花葉序的數學模型<ref>{{Cite journal|last =Vogel| first =H| title =A better way to construct the sunflower head| journal =Mathematical Biosciences| issue =44| pages =179–189| year =1979| doi =10.1016/0025-5564(79)90080-4| volume =44}}</ref>。於[[极坐标系|极坐标系]]的數學式如下：<ref>{{cite book| last =Prusinkiewicz| first =Przemyslaw| authorlink =Przemyslaw Prusinkiewicz| author2 =Lindenmayer, Aristid| authorlink2 =Aristid Lindenmayer| title =The Algorithmic Beauty of Plants| publisher =Springer-Verlag| year =1990| location =| pages =101–107| url =http://algorithmicbotany.org/papers/#webdocs| doi =| isbn =978-0-387-97297-8| access-date =2017-09-17| archive-date =2007-05-19| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20070519020605/http://algorithmicbotany.org/papers/#webdocs| dead-url =no}}</ref>
:<math>r = c \sqrt{n},</math>
:<math>\theta = n \times 137.5^{\circ},</math>
:其中
::<math>\theta</math>為「發散角」（divergence angle）、圓心角
::<math>r</math>為距中心的半徑或距離
::<math>n</math>為[[自然數|自然數]]，花葉序的指數
::<math>c</math>為恆定比例因數

